description: The main philosophy of XPAYPro tokens is the collection of small funds and their transformation into large investments. With the MYDEX PLATFORM Web and mobile application, it is targeted to reach 10 million users and an annual income of 100 million dollars. These revenues are the total of store revenues, revenues collected from advertisers on the platform, and sales of application contents and revenues. In the exchanges where XPAYPro tokens are listed, all revenues are used for repurchase.
name: XPAY Pro Token
